text.tspan: Based on the expert assessments and index by V-Dem. It captures the extent to which people are free from
government torture, political killings, and forced labor; they have property rights; and enjoy the freedoms of movement,
religion, expression, and association. The variable ranges from 0 to 1 (most rights).
Data source: OWID based on V-Dem (v13)
